short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Working with too many tabs. Switch between the most recently used tabs and last recently used using keyboard shortcut

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Working with too many tabs. Now switch between them efficiently using the custom keyboard shortcut. 
Features:
- Switch to last used tab using the keyboard shortcut ***Ctrl + Q*** (Can be changed)
- See the list of tabs sorted in Most Recently Used order, and switch to the tabs using the keyboard. To open the list of tabs use Ctrl + E(can be changed).

For feature request or to report a bug, contact shubham2892@gmail.com. Would love to hear from you.
